      "content": "it just feels like i'm putting them through an endless cycle of misery because of me. i keep telling myself things will change but i'm just lying to myself and them. wouldn't it be more merciful to just stop the cycle now? to give them the chance to be happy without me being the reason they're always struggling? it feels like the only way i can actually do something good for them is to just be gone.",
